Report 3: API Development & Business Registration

Authentication System:
  - Created API Key Header authentication
  - Built get_current_business() dependency for protected routes
  - Added API key format validation
  - Implemented business status checking (active/suspended)
  - Added admin toekn verification for admin endpoints

CRUD operations (Create, Read, Update, Delete):
  - Created business CRUD functions (get_by_email. get_by_id, create)
  - Built API key generation and rotation functions
  - Implemented business category functions
  - Created customer matching functions (finds customers via hashes)
  - Built customer creation with PII hashing
  - Implemented grade calculation and update functions
  - Created chargeback CRUD functions with automatic grade updates

Business API Endpoints:
  - POST /api/v1/businesses/register - Register new business
  - GET /api/v1/businesses/me - Get authenticated business profile
  - POST /api/v1/businesses/rotate-api-key - Rotate API key for security
  - GET /api/v1/categories - List all business categories
  - POST /api/v1/categories/create - Create custom category

Main Application Updates:
  - Added error handling
  - Configured CORS middleware
  - Included business router with proper prefixing
  - Added startup/shutdown event handlers
  - Enhanced health with database verification

Error Handling & Validation:
  - Duplicate email prevention
  - Invalid category ID validation
  - API key format validation
  - Business status checking
  - Error messages

Testing & Verification:
  - Fixed database schema/model mismatches
  - Verified business registration works
  - Tested API key authentication
  - Confirmed all endpoints return proper responses
  - Database connection tested and stable


